===Proverb===
'''[[pride]] [[comes]] [[before]] a [[fall]]'''

# One who is too [[proud]] and [[overconfident]] about their [[abilities]] will often suffer a [[setback]] or [[failure]] which demonstrates that they are not as clever as they think.

